# radroots_simplex_smp_proto

This is the README for `radroots_simplex_smp_proto`, which provides SimpleX SMP
wire protocol primitives for the `radroots` core libraries.

## Overview

 * URI, server address, queue mode, and default port types for SMP endpoints;
 * protocol version constants and related compatibility bounds;
 * wire message, command, and protocol error types for SMP exchanges;
 * portable shared models with optional serialization and shared type export
   support.

